                                                                  Private</h4>
                                                                <p class="small text-secondary mb-0">Your files are
                                                                  processed locally and securely. No data is stored or
                                                                  shared without your permission.</p>
                                                              </div>
                                                            </div>
                                                          </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                      </div>
            </div>
